title: [Pane in the Glass]
description: Scraps of tapestries and assorted linens cover the walls of this ramshackle tent, lending an a impressive array of colors to the otherwise sparse decorations.  Assorted boxes and crates have been indiscriminately arranged to assemble a makeshift storefront with a large frosted glass display case and an unfinished black cherry cabinet placed just behind the tent's stout ironwood support pole.
